<milestone n="1" unit="juan"/>
<lb n="0886a14" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0886a15" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0886a16" ed="T"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="open"><cb:mulu n="001" type="卷"/><cb:jhead><note n="0886001" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">【原】明本，此經與麗本異同甚繁故別載</note>百千印陀羅尼經</cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb n="0886a17" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0886a18" ed="T"/><byline cb:type="Translator">唐于闐三藏實叉難陀譯</byline>
<lb n="0886a19" ed="T"/><cb:div type="jing"><p xml:id="pT21p0886a1901">如是我聞。一時佛在王舍城耆闍崛山中。與
<lb n="0886a20" ed="T"/>大比丘眾及無量菩薩俱。爾時世尊告諸比
<lb n="0886a21" ed="T"/>丘有陀羅尼名百千印。當共受持。誦此呪時。
<lb n="0886a22" ed="T"/>應先歸命金色廣顏光明幢佛。釋迦牟尼佛。
<lb n="0886a23" ed="T"/>即說根本陀羅尼曰。</p>
<lb n="0886a24" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0886a2401" cb:type="dharani">怛姪他<note place="inline">一</note>唵<note place="inline">引聲二</note>菩提菩提菩提菩提<note place="inline">三</note>薩婆怛
<lb n="0886a25" ed="T"/>他揭多瞿折囉<note place="inline">四</note>馱囉馱囉<note place="inline">五</note>訶囉訶囉<note place="inline">六</note>鉢
<lb n="0886a26" ed="T"/>囉呵囉鉢囉呵囉<note place="inline">七</note>莫訶菩提質多<note place="inline">八</note>注盧注
<lb n="0886a27" ed="T"/>盧<note place="inline">九</note>設多曷審彌珊招地低<note place="inline">十</note>薩婆怛他揭多
<lb n="0886a28" ed="T"/>地瑟他<note place="inline">長聲</note>阿毘瑟低<note place="inline">十一</note>具儜具那鉢底<note place="inline">十二</note>
<lb n="0886a29" ed="T"/>勃陀具那婆娑<note place="inline">下去</note>嘶<note place="inline">十三</note>蔑囇蔑囇<note place="inline">十四</note>伽伽
<pb n="0886b" xml:id="T21.1369b.0886b" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0886b01" ed="T"/>那怛囇<note place="inline">十五</note>薩婆怛他揭多地瑟恥低那婆薩
<lb n="0886b02" ed="T"/>怛囇<note place="inline">十六</note>睒摩睒摩<note place="inline">十七</note>鉢囉睒摩鉢囉睒摩<note place="inline">十
<lb n="0886b03" ed="T"/>八</note>薩婆播波鉢囉睒摩寧<note place="inline">十九</note>薩婆播波毘戍
<lb n="0886b04" ed="T"/>達寧<note place="inline">二十</note>虎盧虎盧菩提末伽三鉢囉嘶替低
<lb n="0886b05" ed="T"/><note place="inline">二十一</note>薩婆怛他揭多鉢囉底瑟恥多戍提薩婆
<lb n="0886b06" ed="T"/>訶<note n="0886002" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔二十二〕－【宋】</note><note n="0886002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">二十二【大】，〔－〕【宋】</note><app n="0886002"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">二十二</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0886b07" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0886b0701">爾時世尊。復為大眾說心呪曰。</p>
<lb n="0886b08" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0886b0801" cb:type="dharani">唵<note n="0886003" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔一〕－【宋】【元】</note><note n="0886003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">一【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】</note><app n="0886003"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">一</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>薩婆怛他揭多吠婆盧吉帝<note place="inline"><note n="0886004" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">二＝一【宋】</note><note n="0886004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">二【大】，一【宋】</note><app n="0886004"><lem wit="【大】">二</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">一</rdg></app></note>社耶社
<lb n="0886b09" ed="T"/>耶薩婆訶<note n="0886005" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔三〕－【宋】【元】</note><note n="0886005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">三【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】</note><app n="0886005"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">三</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0886b10" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0886b1001">爾時世尊。復更宣說隨心呪曰。</p>
<lb n="0886b11" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0886b1101" cb:type="dharani">唵虎嚧虎嚧<note place="inline">一</note><g ref="#CB04083"/>耶目磎薩婆訶<note n="0886006" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔二〕－【宋】【元】</note><note n="0886006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">二【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】</note><app n="0886006"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">二</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0886b12" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0886b1201">若有比丘比丘尼優婆塞優婆夷及餘淨信善
<lb n="0886b13" ed="T"/>男女等造塔之時。書此陀羅尼句置於塔中。
<lb n="0886b14" ed="T"/>便得具足造百千塔殊勝功德無異。時諸比
<lb n="0886b15" ed="T"/>丘天龍八部一切眾會。聞佛所說歡喜奉行。</p>
<lb n="0886b16" ed="T"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="close"><cb:jhead>百千印陀羅尼經</cb:jhead></cb:juan></cb:div>
